headline: Will Tractor Supply's Margins Hold Steady Amid Rising Supply Costs?
summary: TSCO navigates rising product, transport and tariff costs, with disciplined pricing and cost control to protect margins as it eyes 2026 expansion.

headline: Tractor Supply Paper Clover Campaign Gives the Gift of Opportunity to 4-H Youth
summary: BRENTWOOD, Tenn., November 25, 2025--Tractor Supply Company (NASDAQ: TSCO), the largest rural lifestyle retailer in the United States, continues its ongoing support of 4-H youth nationwide with the kickoff of its winter Paper Clover campaign. Beginning today and extending through December 14, customers can "purchase" a clover at checkout in stores or at TractorSupply.com to directly benefit the organization.
